## German state-wide Forschungsdatenmanagement network links

Baden-Württemberg: [https://bwfdm.scc.kit.edu](https://bwfdm.scc.kit.edu)
Bayern: [https://www.fdm-bayern.org](https://www.fdm-bayern.org)
Berlin: [https://www.bbaw.de/en/research/forschungsdatenmanagement-research-data-management](https://www.bbaw.de/en/research/forschungsdatenmanagement-research-data-management)
Brandenburg: [https://fdm-bb.de](https://fdm-bb.de)
Bremen: [https://www.bremen-research.de](https://www.bremen-research.de)
Hamburg: ?
Hessen: [https://www.uni-marburg.de/en/hefdi](https://www.uni-marburg.de/en/hefdi)
Mecklenburg-Vorpommern: [https://datenkompass-mv.de](https://datenkompass-mv.de)
Niedersachsen: [https://fdm-nds.de](https://fdm-nds.de)
Nordrhein-Westfalen: [https://www.fdm.nrw](https://www.fdm.nrw)
Rheinland-Pfalz: [https://fdm.rlp.net](https://fdm.rlp.net)
Saarland: ?
Sachsen: [https://saxfdm.de](https://saxfdm.de)
Sachsen-Anhalt: ?
Schleswig-Holstein: [https://fdm-sh.de](https://fdm-sh.de)
Thüringen: [https://forschungsdaten-thueringen.de](https://forschungsdaten-thueringen.de)

For University research data management departments please refer to the NFDI List:
[https://www.forschungsdaten.org/index.php/FDM-Kontakte](https://www.forschungsdaten.org/index.php/FDM-Kontakte)

## Other Countries Research Data Management network links
